nodes.text: Lanesord was a female Human who served as a supply officer in the Imperial Army of the Sith Empire. During the Battle of Corellia in the Galactic War, she was stationed at the Imperial war camp in the Labor Valley region of the planet Corellia, distributing stimulants and medical supplies to other Imperial forces.
Supply Officer Lanesord appears in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, released by BioWare in 2011, as a Stims Vendor for Imperial players on Corellia.
